    "year": 2025,
    "notes": [
      "Field codes use format: taxpayer/spouse (e.g., 158/172)",
      "Some fields have 3 codes: taxpayer/spouse/joint (e.g., 305/205/167)",
      "Right column = registered spouse (בן הזוג הרשום), Left column = other spouse",
      "This schema focuses on fields relevant to salaried workers (שכירים)"
